Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.55,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ワープでループなこの想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.30,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何もかもを巻き込んだ想像で遊ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.01,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}アル晴レタ日ノ事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:55.68,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}魔法以上のユカイが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:00.98,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限りなく降りそそぐ　不可能じゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:06.82,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明日また会うとき　笑いながらハミング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:09.95,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}嬉しさを集めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:12.49,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}カンタンなんだよ　こ{\fe134\fn方正准圆简体\fs23}·{\r}ん{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}な{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:17.08,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}追いかけてね　つかまえてみて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:21.00,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大きな夢＆夢　スキでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:34.04,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就像是那地球仪上各种谜团　都一一解说开来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:37.75,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家就能随心所欲地到处旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:40.21,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想一直到时间尽头Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:44.55,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那想法像变成圆圈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.30,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管什么都要把这一切卷进幻想里面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.01,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在那晴空之下的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:55.68,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是比魔法还更加愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:00.98,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}永无尽头地倾注到世界　一切皆有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:06.82,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明天再与你见面之时　带着灿烂笑容轻松哼唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:09.95,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把那些喜悦收集起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:12.49,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这些其实都非常　简·单·容·易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:17.08,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}赶快追上去吧　试着抓住它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:21.00,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那雄伟的梦想＆梦想　你喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:31.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,答えはいつも私の胸に...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:47.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんでだろ　あなたを選んだ私です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:53.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もうとまらない　運命様から決められたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:59.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe　真似だけじゃつまらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:08.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,感じるまま感じることだけをするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:15.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,冒険でしょでしょ！ホントが嘘に変わる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:22.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,夢があるから強くなるのよ　誰の為じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一緒に来てくださいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:31.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまでも自由な私を見てよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:36.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,明日過去になった今日のいまが奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:43.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,つかもう未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:48.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:31.27,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,这份答案一直存在于我的内心里...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:47.12,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟为什么　选择你的居然会是区区的我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:53.46,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,已不能停步　虽然能让高贵的命运来决定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:59.72,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe　单纯的模仿一定十分无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.05,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:08.48,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,照着感觉走　只去做那感觉到的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:15.32,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险对吧对吧！在真实变成了谎言的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:22.20,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,若能够拥有梦想　就可以收获坚强　并不是为了谁而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.54,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,就请你与我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:31.25,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,而看着这个无论何处都会是自由的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:36.67,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天变成过去之前将此日此时的那奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:43.14,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,牢牢抓住面向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:48.77,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  朝比奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五月份春日建立SOS团之后光阴飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经是六月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实在这段时间里面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经被卷入了很多将我的世界观完全推翻的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那些先放在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是这样一个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位！我们要参加棒球大赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起直到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有发生什么值得一提的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在享受着悠闲的平静与无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看来那段日子也只是转瞬即逝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至于为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这家伙一旦这样一脸高兴地笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么我就会变成疲劳的线操人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要参加什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第九届室内业余棒球大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  是谁要去参加这个草地棒球赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.58,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（草地棒球：外行人参加的以尽兴为目的的棒球比赛）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是我们了！这还用问？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你所谓的「我们」是不是把我们几个也算进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还需要再找4个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时一样  是个不把对自己的想法有异议的话听进耳朵的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂棒球的规则吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这我当然知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹我也是尝试参加过棒球社的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多少懂一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然因为一点意思都没有所以很快就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们为什么还非要参加\N这种「一点意思都没有」的棒球大赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是让全天下知道我们存在的大好机会啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能在比赛中获胜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许SOS团的名号能够一举独步天下呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机会难得啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  是个好主意吧  实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？棒球很不错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先说清楚  我们的目标是最终胜利！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一场比赛都不许输！因为我最讨厌失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么干脆地就答应了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也应该提出一点反驳意见吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起到处乱转去寻找外星人或者UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（UMA：Unidentified Mysterious Animals，未知生物）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这个活动要健康得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  这个比赛什么时候开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是后天吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说时间也太紧了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已经报名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,队伍名称我已经报好是「SOS团」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我可是决不会出错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的4个队员你打算从哪里挖啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要随便逮几个在那些到处闲晃的人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真这么说的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  你先别轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之…谷口和国木田好像满闲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她用「那些」来称呼同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…还剩下两个人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…如果我的朋友也可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就也算上那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像什么人都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈学姐的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点放心不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么「时候」  什么「地方」交的朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在这个时间…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在班上认识的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我也来推荐一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上  我认识的一个人对我们的事很感兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的人选由我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然决定好了就马上来特训吧！特训！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特训？现在就开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我们就要去参加棒球比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个答案很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是  只不过是因为春日她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点烦闷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个地方借给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有棒球用具也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？你说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们必须要赶快进行棒球训练嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们比较碍事  闪开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么可能答应啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛！只借一阵子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是容易被看穿的青春时期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先打个一千棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这球上可寄托了SOS团的未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好接住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次听说我们的未来原来是寄托在这么小的一个球上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠  要来了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还站得起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和我感情这么好的话  又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！阿虚！实玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们受伤退场！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面棒球社的给我补上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的正好是打了一千棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是连这个都能数得一清二楚的你比较令我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  长门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛当天能不能让老天下场雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是能让比赛中止的那种大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对局部性的环境资料进行篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有对行星生态系统造成后遗症的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,后遗症是…大约多久以后会发作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,几百年到一万年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是别这么做比较好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  比赛当天来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…其实不来临也没什么问题的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是阿虚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常听实玖瑠提起你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  这位是我的朋友鹤屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是谷口  请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是国木田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀～阿虚是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的请求我实在没办法拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是谷口和国木田对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}这是我们的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙你也想让她上场打球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说「那种家伙」也太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说可也是我的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自我介绍说是「小学五年级生  现在10岁」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个坦率到无法联想到是你妹妹一般的好孩子呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过重点在于我们参加的可是一般年龄层的棒球赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是青少年级的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊春日小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会把妹妹带来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说本来就不可能打赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这可是春日搞出来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一不小心真的最终胜出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会变成超级麻烦的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果混一个小学五年级生进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样能赢才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好稍微放一下水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果赢得太狠也就太不给对手面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像她还真的想要打赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有决定打击顺序和守备位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个来决定！没有意见了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有打击的顺序和防守的位置两种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外我是投手和一棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想好的只有决定的方法吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么  你有什么不满意的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是民主的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古希腊可是还用抽签来选政治家呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别把古希腊的政治制度\N和现代日本的草地棒球打击顺序混为一谈好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有你可以按照兴趣来选择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算什么民主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:57.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,名字      守备位置\N一棒  凉宫春日  投手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:58.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,二棒  实玖瑠    右外野\N三棒  有希      中间手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:09:59.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,四棒  阿虚      二垒手\N五棒  虚妹      左外野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.41,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,六棒  古泉      捕手\N七棒  国木田    一垒手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,八棒  鹤屋      三垒手\N九棒  谷口      游击手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来能够更快地回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚刚听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一场的对手是叫做「上上原海盗」的大学生球队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是本届大赛的种子队伍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只要得分相差10分就会提前结束比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就开始准备回家应该也不算早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Play Ball！{\r}\N比赛开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他投的球完全没什么好怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都跟上来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这厮对着朝比奈学姐投得是什么该死的球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我打到她身上一个看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就去跟你们群殴！把这里变成群殴狂欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使劲打啊！使劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！为什么不挥棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有希！如果不挥棒的话不是就更不会打中了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚  你一定要打中啊！你可是四棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（一般四棒的位置会安排打击力最强的队员，称之为强打或强棒）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在期待我这个抽签决定的四棒做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春日是面对这种球打出长打的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴！你在做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遗憾！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,严防死守吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Play！{\r}\N比赛继续！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,游刃有余啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Foul ball！{\r}\N界外球！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她只会冲着好球区投直球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被人看出来当然会被打中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们守备的漏洞比热带大草原上蚁巢的还要多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竹筐一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一回合总算是把失分控制在2分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因为对方的胜利女神来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天谁都希望休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  第二轮的攻势也是毫无悬念地结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:40.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后又很干脆地被对方拿下了几分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来下一回合就可以结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Out！{\r}\N出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太难了吧  光是让球棒打到球就用尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是需要那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}　Time{\r}\N先暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凉宫同学…不  不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了！快点给我脱好换衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠  可以拍下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是绑个马尾比较好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  来加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么做～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  大声加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各  各位！请打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们了  加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的～包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种球果然还是打不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  反正也没指望你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安全上垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠！这次一定要打中哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}上吧！实玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}朝比奈学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠！这个啊  用这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这样能让对方投手的MP减少吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来好像是在打暗号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决定过什么暗号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想那大概是叫她用抢分战术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（抢分战术：跑者在三垒时，打击手使用牺牲打令跑者得以回本垒的战术）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二人出局还打抢分战术的暗号？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那个永世教练也会用更常识性的战术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（永世教练：指巨人队的长岛教练，\N巨人队时代教练都由长岛家的人担任而得名。被很多球迷厌恶）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是发现了朝比奈打中球的几率基本上是零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是因此做出意义不明的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,故意让对方看透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会令内野手出现失误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或是希望朝比奈同学用牺牲打打中球的话也能有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然完全被人家看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实玖瑠  你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后咬紧牙关！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是惩罚  惩罚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让大家看看你这张可笑的脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是打出莫名其妙暗号的你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去盗本垒不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然不想听  不过你姑且说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个前所未有的大规模封闭空间开始产生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还正在以非常快的速度扩大着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要凉宫同学的心情不恢复  它就会持续扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「那个」也就会继续大肆破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为打输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不懂事的小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你说得好像是别人的事情一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这和你也有很大的关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为决定打击顺序的时候我们不是抽签了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而作为结果  你是四棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不觉得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为凉宫同学这样希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才成为了第四棒打击手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  你完全没有起到四棒的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  这一回合尽全力令比赛不要提前结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在比赛结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就等同于世界末日来临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！要开始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何  都要把失分控制在两分以内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两人出局  跑者在一  二垒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在零对九
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一分就会强制结束比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶上啊  要赶上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice Play！干得不错嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的好友！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸凑得太近了  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你上次和凉宫同学一起到那个世界去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎么回来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我想起那件事来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用那一招的话  也许又能够顺利解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就用些能够确保胜利的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和她之间的利害关系应该也是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长门同学终于也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她做了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像在咏唱咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咒文？那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…这是禁止谈论的事项
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咒文吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊！你怎么有这么大的力气？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  对属性信息作了能力提升改写
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,制导模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飞得好远！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  制导模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  乱来也要有点限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  再这样下去就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在各种意义上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才忘记说了  第一场比赛时间限制为90分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以已经没有下一回合了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要守住这一回合  我们就获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？就这样获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不获胜不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏如此  封闭空间的扩大速度似乎已经降下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果在这里被对方逆转局势的话可就再见滑铁卢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过猜那个时候春日心情如何也没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我有个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常当真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要把这一回合的失分控制在最低
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Ball！{\r}\N坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你给我好好投！难得我和你交换位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果输了的话就罚你请所有人吃饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  我投的球可是负担着全世界的命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这个世界还真是不值钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于这Mysterious Ball（命名：我）的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来世界不需要被毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}S…Strike two！{\r}\N两…两好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的打击手也很无聊地被三球三振了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕会已经成为最后的打击手的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也已经两好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Strike two！{\r}\N两好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚  还有一球  决出胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不说这球也会决定胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  上上原海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,侥幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不死三振了！长门！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（不死三振：在一垒无人情况下，\N捕手未能接到应该能将打击手三振的球时，打击手安全冲上一垒）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去捡起球来投过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这一群人稍微有点超乎常理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Ga…game and set！{\r}\N比…比赛结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（日文的省略读法读作「Game set」）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然由于长门的作弊式魔法我们打赢了这一场…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二场要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果就这样继续打第二场的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有些对不起上上原海盗  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也差不多该去给「同伴」们帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话人数也不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弃权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不能让凉宫同学闲下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就作为今后的课题吧  有研究的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也玩够了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉说有急事要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腿和手臂也都累得动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你觉得可以  那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有些饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃午饭吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太感谢你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你这根球棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己都没有注意到过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我有打棒球的天分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是长门有希？听实玖瑠她经常提到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家尽量多吃点吧  今天阿虚请客～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我口袋里也有一笔临时收入了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我衷心期盼上上原海盗队能拿下傲人战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐生！好好打！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉来迟啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这次参加哪个好？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,足球和美式橄榄球都是多少人参加的运动？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只用之前的那些人够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一面看着春日最美丽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始考虑哪个是人数最少的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美式橄榄球…不！去给我打门球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.81,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（一种只需要5个人的球类运动）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:16.91,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[三种不同的茶杯…这个细节我都不记得了OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:44.73,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[不带眼镜的长门大明神啊～！（大心）]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:51.19,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…而现在那套女仆装已经用衣架挂起来，吊在社团活动室的角落了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.48,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「因为没有人有任何反应，所以一如往常还是由我勉为其难地反问春日。\N为什么大家老是把我当成和春日沟通的管道？\N再没有任何事情比这个任务更让我伤脑筋的了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.37,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「主办单位是市公所，似乎是历史悠久、每年都会举办的活动」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:30.87,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「我全身一阵虚脱」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:46.43,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「而且春日会锁定的人除了一个例外，向来都不是普通人。\N那个极少数的例外就是我。而我并不打算再认识更多来历不明的人了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.39,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[（春日：）「总比没有好」]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.07,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[这里特别配合台版小说翻译成“烦闷”…不过其实还是无聊比较准确OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:40.04,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「你好歹也多动一点吧。还是我该夸奖你动态视力极佳呢？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.84,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…一个不规则弹跳的硬球掠过我的手套，\N穿过我的胯下，直接命中了朝比奈的膝盖。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.10,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「又会怎样？我耸耸肩。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.65,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「好久远的未来啊」]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.25,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[等过了暑假保准你不会再这么说。]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.50,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[通称：虚妹]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.83,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[上上原海盗是台版小说的翻译，\N原文“上ヶ原パイレーツ”，感觉译作“上原海盗”就可以了…]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.40,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「春日气势汹汹地大叫。可是，她这种做法完全是反效果。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.20,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「因为这么一来，对方选手对女生手下留情的心情早就消失得无影无踪了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.87,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[原文“乱闘パーティー”…难道是在EG“乱○派对”？！]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.65,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…事实上，我感觉投手投出球的那一刹那，球就已经进入捕手的手套里了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.83,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「哇！球转弯了。这就是所谓的曲球吗？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.34,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「春日带着仿佛被伊阿宋背叛的美狄亚公主般的眼神，\N看着在内也跑了一圈的对方第三棒打击手」\N（和动画略有不同）]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:27.49,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「（春日）发现我投注过去的视线之后，\N她把嘴巴嘟得像鸭子一样尖，放弃弄头发了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.28,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[“脑”]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.09,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「古泉带着与充满危机感的说话内容完全不搭调的表情说着」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.26,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[苦啊！苦啊！]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.71,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「SELECT serial code FROM database WHERE code data ORDER BY 攻击性信息战斗 HAVING terminate mode。\Npersonal name 朝仓凉子，判断为敌性。\N解除该对象的有机信息连接。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:49.75,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[按原文看来貌似长门是在对某“主机”下达指令，\N（如上我所写的）大写的部分是命令格式，小写和中文部分是具体参数吧…]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.62,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[「…因为我觉得对方选手的视线不在我们这些选手身上，\N反倒全集中在这支球棒上了。…」]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.75,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,[搞不好对方也打算开群殴派对…？]
